message.body: Sorry for getting back to you so late. I'm going to be busy around 11AM to 2PMish. Can you meet after then?
Of course! Thank you! Sorry for changing the day this week :( where is convenient?
Don't worry about it. I have to be around University City around that time, but I don't really care where we meet.
Thank you! If I can wake up early enough, i'll probably go to the art museum. So please text me when you become free:)
Do you know when you'll be free today?
I was thinking about eating with my friends later. Do you want to come?
I'm free all day today:p and i'd like to eat with your friends. are you free now?
Uh...not now. Where are you though?
I'm walking around south street! Should I head to university city?
Uh..could you? Also, what do you want to eat?
of course! :) well, ill think an tell you later!
Okay, let me know when you're around Drexel. I'm at 33rd and Market right now.
